            "description": "One of the most pressing and complicated issues that European regions face nowadays is how to introduce and develop Research and Innovation (R&I) regional policies that promote sustainable development and achieve societal inclusion and citizen participation, under a framework of democratic governance. This is the so-called \u201cRegional Dilemma\u201d. The aim of RRI2SCALE Project is to directly address the Dilemma of four pilot European participating territories: Hordaland (Norway), Overijssel (Netherlands), Kriti (Greece) and Galicia (Spain) by empowering the regional ecosystems and boosting their development trajectories in the R&I domain.",
